import random
import unittest


def remainder(a, b):
    return a % b


class TestRemainder(unittest.TestCase):
    def test_random(self):
        a = random.randint(1, 10)
        b = random.randint(1, 10)
        expected = a % b
        actual = remainder(a, b)
        self.assertEqual(actual, expected)


if __name__ == "__main__":
    unittest.main()
